name: TDMQuery
0:
”Alexa ask my lane cost to get me planned cost from morton”
”Alexa ask my lane cost to get me planned cost from morton to peoria for year 2017 and month January”
”Alexa ask my lane cost get me planned cost from morton to peoria for 2017 April”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my lane cost
des:
This skill queries for a particular lane(Origin and Destination) and year and month. It shows plan cost for the same lane and year and month
For example you can say: get me planned cost from morton to peoria for year 2017 and month January
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
